{"tid":913562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"單親媽雇人「假扮生父」　騙女兒10年還想繼續演","createTime":"2018-11-23T13:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T14:26:43.000Z","uid":212399,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fe26dc21684b08260881d666427b452bb3715602","tid":913562,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3715/3715815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3715%2F3715815.jpg&h=7600bb61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單親媽最後甚至愛上雇來的假爸爸<br />\n有些單親家庭的爸媽會對兒女懷有愧疚感，因此就出現一項新職業「代理爸爸」，每個月會和孩子見一次面，陪伴小孩吃飯、玩樂等等，做所有爸爸應該做的事。日本小妹妹惠美（Megumi）就以為代理爸爸是自己生父，10年來對真相渾然不知。<br />\n據BBC報導，惠美從小就由媽媽麻子（Asako）帶大，但始終很好奇爸爸是誰，甚至會責怪自己害爸爸離開。麻子後來還發現女兒在學校會因為單親而遭到霸凌，「她變得不愛說話，很沉默且退縮。」<br />\n麻子認為，單親家庭的孩子在日本社會中較容易受到歧視，連學校老師也束手無策。她不忍心再看女兒如此傷心，剛好聽說有專門派送員，會幫忙假扮成婚宴客人、約會對象等等，於是就決定聘請員工高橋（Takashi）來假裝是惠美的生父。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3715/3715816.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3715%2F3715816.jpg&h=f88fbc82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女兒至今還以為對方是自己親生爸爸<br />\n高橋過去有假扮男朋友、商人、爸爸和朋友的經驗，並在5場假婚禮上當過新郎。他得知惠美的家庭狀況後，透過觀看多部電影還瞭解如何扮演好爸爸，「我會記住電影中的對話，幫助我了解不同的家庭型態。」<br />\n麻子告訴女兒，爸爸雖然後來再婚有了新家庭，但最近又重心聯絡上她們，甚至想和母女倆見面。惠美起初很驚訝，但實際見面後相處得非常融洽，每個月還會一起去看電影，這段關係就這樣持續了10年之久。<br />\n惠美也因為假爸爸的出現變得更樂觀開朗，但想要維持這種和諧代價並不便宜。每次見面麻子就要支付高橋1萬日幣（約台幣3000元），最後甚至還愛上了假爸爸，高橋則是很明確的表示，自己和母女倆只有利益交換的關係。<br />\n麻子提到，不想要破壞3人現在的關係，也不打算告訴女兒真相，「當惠美結婚的時候，我希望高橋也在場，甚至等到惠美生小孩，他還能繼續扮演成爺爺。」"},{"pid":"f49992590aaebd11c100c3eb266fb661c6633966","tid":913562,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d9edba01473ffbdefb256fb45c7f3bc97cef83","tid":913562,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867515a6febc87972258f03c121a373adff88018","tid":913562,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:26:12.000Z","msg":"世界奇妙物語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3570c753abb0619e1d566a3bf327cfd99da6537e","tid":913562,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:28:11.000Z","msg":"Dear Frankie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6094c0745e83cd0810bb52205a4af4ca4951eba4","tid":913562,"uid":29606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86e1a432c6dc2c7fa8c9a701ec09c06ebcb1b9bc","tid":913562,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:43:58.000Z","msg":"借個女過橋搵ptbf<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b8f70eb4a6fb26b0ca93bba07dc47664bb6a04","tid":913562,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:45:59.000Z","msg":"美少女夢工廠父嫁結局"},{"pid":"54ef37dcaf26cd16e33866f9822691f84db8dcbe","tid":913562,"uid":103156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:46:00.000Z","msg":"呃到一世就唔算呃"},{"pid":"5ec87d82d44f2eb7d02888d41ece9a0d023ec2dc","tid":913562,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:50:13.000Z","msg":"Explosion !!!"},{"pid":"fba890c106cdf0c4db0abd88c48b3e47d6e6a5a1","tid":913562,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:55:06.000Z","msg":"諗起今年上果套動畫電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ee7837b945a8e91362faf9131a81e5bf3baee5","tid":913562,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:58:12.000Z","msg":"屌你個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c65ddf8688eb2008806010836451a2728a786ee","tid":913562,"uid":214036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d45893a8b54610e667eeb82c7743878c520e40b8","tid":913562,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>並在5場假婚禮上當過新郎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cff0f92f9825642eeb9489640f96ad04954229","tid":913562,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3570c753abb0619e1d566a3bf327cfd99da6537e","tid":913562,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:28:11.000Z","msg":"Dear Frankie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:10:33.000Z","msg":"Frank<br />\n<img src=\"https://bamfstyle.files.wordpress.com/2014/02/catchtux-watch1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbamfstyle.files.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F02%2Fcatchtux-watch1.jpg&h=05606ae9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b73a3aadc7008d8223c0c0162aaafedec94959f","tid":913562,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:13:35.000Z","msg":"我都想搵份pt daddy"},{"pid":"d7c3ffa85aff49fb4eb28230b1a0b6276f014f98","tid":913562,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2df943a3a5b5709e17f1b843a2a5ebff4cf8fc77","tid":913562,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:20:37.000Z","msg":"咁多位早晨，我今日嚟，係想同你哋講個故事嘅：<br />\n<br />\n喺幾年前<br />\n我同一個寡婦結咗婚<br />\n佢有一個已成年嘅女<br />\n後來嫁咗比我老豆<br />\n<br />\n咁我繼女就做咗我後媽<br />\n而我老豆就做咗我女婿<br />\n<br />\n兩年後我老婆同我生咗一個仔<br />\n佢喺我後媽嘅同母異父嘅細佬<br />\n我個仔叫我「老豆」<br />\n我就叫我個仔「舅父」<br />\n<br />\n我繼女又為我老豆生咗一個仔<br />\n佢喺我細佬<br />\n但佢又要叫我外公<br />\n<br />\n我喺我老婆個老公<br />\n但喺我老婆喺我後媽個阿媽喎<br />\n所以我喺自己嘅外公<br />\n<br />\n到咗新年<br />\n嚟料喇<br />\n<br />\n我就同我後媽同我老豆<br />\n即係同我繼女同女婿交換利是<br />\n<br />\n我封廿蚊比我個仔<br />\n佢話：「多謝老豆！」<br />\n我又答返佢：「唔洗，舅父！喺呢，咁我嗰封呢？」<br />\n「你都痴線，我結咗婚喇咩？」唉，我自己都亂咗... <br />\n<br />\n食團年飯嗰陣<br />\n我喺抬面上面放咗一封一千蚊利是<br />\n再拎返封利是上手<br />\n叫咗聲：「多謝外公！」<br />\n<br />\n好彩唔喺街姐<br />\n唔係真係比人捉去青山瞓一排<br />\n而家諗返自己真喺痴痴地線<br />\n自己比錢自己洗<br />\n咪即係去自己鋪頭買野..."},{"pid":"57915fa44d53966b9aa71dc981cee3f5992c2730","tid":913562,"uid":160853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:26:43.000Z","msg":"呢1萬日圓抵到爛"}]}